                            <comment id="192952" author="emoly.liu" created="Fri, 21 Apr 2017 01:47:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Corrected some wrong option usages according to the latest fix and our discussion.&lt;br/&gt;
Please have a review. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="192788" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 20 Apr 2017 08:43:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I updated the PFL user guide per Niu&apos;s comment. The changes include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added commands/example to set default PFL layout to an existing directory&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added all kinds of PFL related &quot;lfs getstripe&quot; commands&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added all kinds of PFL related &quot;lfs find&quot; commands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Please have a check. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="192094" author="niu" created="Fri, 14 Apr 2017 14:13:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think it&apos;s worth to mention that &apos;lfs find support layout component options now, and give some example of set default PFL layout to a directory or mount point.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="192066" author="emoly.liu" created="Fri, 14 Apr 2017 07:18:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just uploaded a new version user guide.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="192064" author="emoly.liu" created="Fri, 14 Apr 2017 06:42:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for Bobi and Niu&apos;s review. I will improve the doc according to your comments.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="192062" author="niu" created="Fri, 14 Apr 2017 06:36:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The way to provide optional argument for &apos;lfs getstripe&apos; is changed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/26491/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/26491/&lt;/a&gt; , you need to update your document, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="192060" author="bobijam" created="Fri, 14 Apr 2017 06:19:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s a great user guide about PFL usage with&#160;graph and example illustration. I made a little&#160;adjustment&#160;recommendation in the uploaded doc.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="190374" author="emoly.liu" created="Sun, 2 Apr 2017 12:55:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=bobijam&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;bobijam&quot;&gt;bobijam&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=niu&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;niu&quot;&gt;niu&lt;/a&gt;, could you please review the PFL user guide I attached here? I added some examples according to the latest PFL patch and our discussion. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="184905" author="emoly.liu" created="Wed, 15 Feb 2017 02:30:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here are some pieces of information about PFL I got from Bobijam:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;wiki page: &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PFL/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PFL/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;patches: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/24851&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/24851&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;branch: pfl under fs/lustre-release&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
